<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>担子；重担；(精神) 负担：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>carry / ease / share the burden</strong>
担负/减轻/分担重担</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The burden of government sits heavily on my shoulders.
治理国家的重担落在我的肩上。</p><footer>人教⑩ – 2</footer></div></div>